#

Spicy Mango Guacamole

10 min
$5
180 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerDipHealthy

Description

A refreshing and zesty twist on classic guacamole, perfect for dipping or as a topping!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • ripe mango: 1
  • red onion: 1/4 cup, finely chopped
  • fresh cilantro: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • jalapeño: 1, finely chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
